39:50.071 --> 39:58.183
say disciplinary, no AWLs for a long time. We had 
less maintenance, deadline vehicles. And by all

40:02.208 --> 40:13.024
of the measurements, and we'd have our 
commander's conference, and the division

40:02.208 --> 40:13.024
headquarters always had all of these different 
disciplinary items on the wall. And we were always

40:16.782 --> 40:19.287
the lowest. The highest was the paratroopers. 
