recommended. Sure. And so the division commander 
gave me a high-efficiency report and recommended

40:50.006 --> 40:58.735
me for General Lawson. And that's another one the 
board meets. If this individual had been

41:00.777 --> 41:03.379
recommended, by a number of general officers. And 
